    <!-- To change
     - Edit trunk/maven-skin/src/main/resources/css/screen.css      
     - Run mvn install in trunk/maven-skin/ to get changed screen.css in $HOME/.m2/repository/org/hippoecm/hippo-ecm-maven-skin/2.01.00-SNAPSHOT/hippo-ecm-maven-skin-2.01.00-SNAPSHOT.jar 
     - Run mvn -N site in trunk/ to use the new screen.css

     Possible Errors:

     - Changes not in effect after using trunk/maven-skin/ for mvn -N site.
     - Takes longer using trunk/ for mvn install.
     - `[INFO] Checking for local modifications: skipped' in listing is not an error.
    -->
    <!-- Example of of default skin from maven
     <groupId>org.apache.maven.skins</groupId>
     <artifactId>maven-classic-skin</artifactId>
